section.heading: Uniform Interstate Family Support Act.
section.text: This chapter may be cited as the Uniform Interstate Family Support Act.

annotations.annotation: For temporary (90 days) enactment of this chapter, see §§ 101-903 of the Uniform Interstate Family Support Congressional Emergency Act of 2016 (D.C. Act 21-301, Feb. 18, 2016, 63 DCR 2139).
For temporary (90 days) enactment of this chapter, see §§ 101-903 of the Uniform Interstate Family Support Emergency Act of 2015 (D.C. Act 21-215, Nov. 30, 2015, 62 DCR 15616).
